node.title: Probe underway after massive Matamata blaze
node.description: The fire was in a manufacturing building.
node.content: ["A large fire at a manufacturing building overnight in Matamata is being investigated.\n", "Emergency services were called to a blaze at Viking Kayaks on Firth St just after 9pm on Saturday.", "Ten fire trucks had attended the scene and fire crews had the blaze under control by 10pm and fully extinguished by 1am.", "Fire investigators were at the scene on Sunday morning.", "RNZ"]
